{
  "stem": "1603.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember what it was, but then we opened it, and we ate it, and we felt like in heaven, like you would go to the best Hungarian or American restaurant in America and have a $500 dinner.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "OK, that's how I felt opening and eating that canned food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, how that canned food tasted, really, I found out that a couple of years later after the war was over and we already ate normally, I found that canned food, bought it, was thrilled.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was thrilled to death to find this heavenly food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when I opened it and tasted it, I spitted it out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was horrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But that's how hungry we were.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I think these two things probably will explain it to you as how hungry we were and-- and by method of luck of getting foods and stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And very rarely, a bakery would be open.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we would be going out and standing in line at the bakery, a long line, for bread.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then low-flying aircraft would come and shoot at us with machine guns while we were standing at the bread.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But we were so hungry that nobody walked away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The airplanes went away, we got up, and whoever died from a machine-gun bullet was dead, and the rest of us waited for our turn to get our bread.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They weren't necessarily Jews, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were all kind of people there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I forgot to-- to mention something, which is very dramatic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was still in this Catholic school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was November 27, 1944, that my father called me in this Catholic school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he told me that the German troops surrounded the ambulance station where he was standing, and he'd be taken away.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
